# 🎥 Anime Recommendation System

## 📌 Objective  
Develop a **recommendation system** using **cosine similarity** to suggest similar anime based on key features.  

## 📊 Dataset  
- **Dataset:** Anime Dataset  
- **Features:**  
   - Anime Title  
   - Broadcast Type  
   - Genre  
   - Number of Episodes  
   - Average User Ratings  
   - Community Member Count  

## 🧠 Techniques Used  
- **Data Preprocessing:**  
   - Handled missing values  
   - Explored dataset structure and attributes  

- **Feature Extraction:**  
   - Selected relevant features for similarity calculation  
   - Encoded categorical variables (e.g., Genre)  
   - Normalized numerical features  

- **Recommendation System:**  
   - Implemented **cosine similarity** for anime recommendations  
   - Recommended similar anime based on similarity scores  
   - Experimented with different similarity thresholds  

## 🔍 Analysis and Interpretation  
- **Significant Features:**  
   - Genres and user ratings heavily influenced recommendations  
   - Adjusting similarity thresholds impacted recommendation diversity  

## 🚀 Results  
- **Accuracy:** Effective similarity-based recommendations  
- **Insights:**  
   - Popular anime had stronger similarity matches  
   - Genre-based recommendations provided meaningful suggestions  

